    "example": "The defense presented mitigating circumstances, including the defendant's lack of criminal history and role as a caretaker for his ill mother, to argue for a lenient sentence. 辩护⽅提出了减罪情节，包括被告没有犯罪前科以及作为 病母看护者的⻆⾊，以争取较宽大的刑罚。",
